  "description": "NOC view of the OSE OTel demo: at-a-glance health on top, producer (HTTP) row, consumer (AMQP) row, topology + RED matrix, and a collapsed drill-down zone for paged operators. Hides docker-compose CLI traces everywhere.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": false,
